表格还款计划表的代码预览

drop index IDX_CONTRACT_ID on USER_RETURNPLAN;

drop index IDX_COMPANY_CODE on USER_RETURNPLAN;

drop index IDX_CUST_CELLPHONE on USER_RETURNPLAN;

drop index IDX_ORDER_ID on USER_RETURNPLAN;

drop table if exists USER_RETURNPLAN;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: USER_RETURNPLAN */
/*==============================================================*/
create table USER_RETURNPLAN
(
ID int not null auto_increment,
ORDER_ID varchar(12) not null,
CONTRACT_ID varchar(18) not null,
CUST_CELLPHONE char(11) not null,
COMPANY_ID char(6) not null,
CURRENT_PERIOD int(2) not null,
TOTAL_PERIOD int(2) not null,
RETURN_STATUS char(1) not null default '0',
RETURN_CHANNEL char(1),
RETURN_DATE date not null,
PRINCIPAL_AMOUNT decimal(10,2) not null,
INTEREST_AMOUNT decimal(10,2) not null,
MANAGEMENT_AMOUNT decimal(10,2) not null,
IS_OVERDUE bit,
OVERDUE_DAYS int,
OVERDUE_AMOUNT decimal(10,2),
RETURN_DATE_AC datetime,
CREATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
UPDATE_TIME datetime not null default CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
primary key (ID)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: IDX_ORDER_ID */
/*==============================================================*/
create index IDX_ORDER_ID on USER_RETURNPLAN
(
ORDER_ID
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: IDX_CUST_CELLPHONE */
/*==============================================================*/
create index IDX_CUST_CELLPHONE on USER_RETURNPLAN
(
CUST_CELLPHONE
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: IDX_COMPANY_CODE */
/*==============================================================*/
create index IDX_COMPANY_CODE on USER_RETURNPLAN
(
COMPANY_ID
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: IDX_CONTRACT_ID */
/*==============================================================*/
create index IDX_CONTRACT_ID on USER_RETURNPLAN
(
CONTRACT_ID
);
